  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>What this bug entails:

We believe that it's too hard to create development environments for most 
projects. We made a draft web app--the buildhelper tab on OpenHatch project 
pages--that makes a checklist for prospective contributors, so they can go 
through the steps one by one. Right now, there's no way to write or edit these 
checklists, though. What this bug will do is implement editing with the 
buildhelper data living inside one large textarea, with a standard text-based 
format. 

This bug would be good for someone who thinks it'd be fun to try to convert user-
inputted text to and from Django ORM objects. As for what format the buildhelper 
text ought to have, we were thinking something vaguely MediaWiki-ish; ask Asheesh 
for more details on that.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
